221
00:20:31,788 --> 00:20:33,625
Park Tae In.

222
00:20:35,290 --> 00:20:37,250
Hej, Park Tae In!

223
00:20:43,095 --> 00:20:44,393
Učitelko Na.

224
00:20:44,491 --> 00:20:46,867
